task.prompt: Write a function to print the first n lucky numbers.
task.gold:
def lucky_num(n):
 List=range(-1,n*n+9,2)
 i=2
 while List[i:]:List=sorted(set(List)-set(List[List[i]::List[i]]));i+=1
 return List[1:n+1]
